OL,7,FLondon has a higher number of baby
OL,8,Fdeaths in hospitals compared to any
OL,9,Fother region in the country, official
OL,10,Ffigures analysed by ITV News London
OL,11,Fshow.
OL,13,FIn the year to March 2023, 394 babies
OL,14,Fin London died within the first month
OL,15,Fof their lives, which are known as
OL,16,F'neonatal deaths'.
OL,18,FIn the same year there were 376
OL,19,F'infant deaths'; children who died
OL,20,Fwhile under the age of one.
