OL,7,FThose figures show a steady increase
OL,8,Fsince 2022.
OL,10,F'Inadequate' maternity care received
OL,11,Fby mothers and their babies during
OL,12,Fpregnancy and labour within some
OL,13,FLondon hospitals could be a reason for
OL,14,Fthe worrying trend.
OL,16,FAcross the capital, seven NHS
OL,17,FMaternity Units 'require improvement'
OL,18,Faccording to the Care Quality
OL,19,FCommission (CQC), and two were ranked
OL,20,F'inadequate'.
