OL,7,FOne London hospital to fall into the
OL,8,F'inadequate' category is North
OL,9,FMiddlesex Hospital in Enfield.
OL,11,FThe CQC updated its independent rating
OL,12,Fof the maternity unit there to
OL,13,F'inadequate' in a report published in
OL,14,FDecember 2023.
OL,16,FThe four-part rating system ranks from
OL,17,F'outstanding' to 'good' to 'requires
OL,18,Fimprovement' to 'inadequate' as the
OL,19,Fworst possible rating.
