OL,7,FITV News London spoke to a family who
OL,8,Fsay they received inadequate care from
OL,9,FNorth Middlesex Hospital.
OL,11,FDue to alleged failings by maternity
OL,12,Fservices there, the birth of Rebecca
OL,13,Fand Dan Whitehouse's son Lucas was
OL,14,Ftraumatic and his health was
OL,15,Fpermanently damaged.
OL,17,FFor nine minutes, Lucas' head was
OL,18,Ftrapped and starved of oxygen.
