OL,7,FThe NHS has since admitted liability,
OL,8,FDan and Jessica even received a letter
OL,9,Ffrom the then-prime minister David
OL,10,FCameron, with words of reassurance.
OL,12,FWhile carrying out research into
OL,13,Fmaternity services across the capital,
OL,14,FITV News London spoke to a midwife at
OL,15,FNorth Middlesex Hospital who was not
OL,16,Fsurprised at the damning outcome of
OL,17,Fthe CQC report in general.
