OL,7,FThe midwife, who asked to remain
OL,8,Fanonymous, said: "Honestly, a lot of
OL,9,Fthem didn't care. I was really quite
OL,10,Fsurprised that they didn't care.
OL,12,F"They were just like, it's nothing to
OL,13,Fdo with me. And that was just quite
OL,14,Fremarkable.
OL,16,F"I read the report then, and I can't
OL,17,Fremember everything that was on there,
OL,18,Fbut I definitely agree with it. There
OL,19,Fwasn't one statement that I thought:
OL,20,F'no, that's not true.'"
