OL,7,FThe midwife recounted examples of her
OL,8,Fconcerns about certain practices by
OL,9,Fmaternity staff during labour.
OL,11,FShe said: "The worst one was a woman
OL,12,Fwho was being induced for post-date.
OL,13,FSo she was overdue.
OL,15,F"Baby on the scans were saying it was
OL,16,Fnormal growth, but every time they
OL,17,Fwere increasing, um, the oxytocin
OL,18,Fdrip, the baby's heart rate would just
OL,19,Fdrop like dramatically.
