OL,7,F"The baby came out very poor and was
OL,8,Falso very small. So the scans weren't
OL,9,Faccurate for whatever reason, and it
OL,10,Ftook a while for that baby to come
OL,11,Fround.
OL,13,F"It did need to then go to out of
OL,14,Fhospital for what we call cooling. I
OL,15,Fdon't know what the actual outcome of
OL,16,Fthat baby was."
OL,18,FThis is one example of what she
OL,19,Fbelieves is an avoidable problem
OL,20,Fduring labour.
