OL,7,FBut the regulator found more systemic
OL,8,Fissues at North Middlesex Hospital
OL,9,Fwhich were putting patients at risk.
OL,11,FProblems like staffing and a culture
OL,12,Fof fear.
OL,14,FThe midwife reiterated these factors -
OL,15,Fdescribing her workplace as somewhere
OL,16,Fwith staffing issues and a culture of
OL,17,Ffear.
