OL,7,FShe said: "Body language, (and)
OL,8,Fcertain verbal language, definitely
OL,9,Fcontributes to the fear of not
OL,10,Fescalating. And there definitely is a
OL,11,Fbullying culture.
OL,13,F"So people would rather save face than
OL,14,Fescalate an issue and potentially save
OL,15,Fa baby and mother's life."
