OL,7,FWhile London is the region with the
OL,8,Fhighest number of baby deaths in
OL,9,Fhospital across England - it is
OL,10,Fimportant to note that it also has the
OL,11,Fhighest population and therefore, a
OL,12,Fhigher number of mothers giving birth
OL,13,Fper capita.
