OL,7,FWhen ITV News London's analysis was
OL,8,Fput to Lenny Byrne, chief nurse at
OL,9,FNorth Middlesex University Hospital,
OL,10,Fhe said: "We've had some specific
OL,11,Finformation from the CQC about our
OL,12,Fmaternity services which we took
OL,13,Fextremely seriously at the time and
OL,14,Fresponded immediately."
OL,16,F"We've got better staffing in place,
OL,17,Fwe've also put in new rules in
OL,18,Fresponse to some of the issues
OL,19,Fidentified and we've got a collective
OL,20,Fapproach to delivering that
OL,21,Fimprovement plan."
